            <section id="section_N10027_N1001F_N10001" id="313">
                <title id="315">System / BIOS Requirements</title>
                <p id="317">The BIOS on each host must support PXE booting for initial
                    installation of the HP Helion OpenStack Carrier Grade software.</p>
                <note id="note_N1050F_N10500_N10027_N1000F_N10001" id="510">
                    <p id="511">Unified Extensible Firmware Interface (UEFI) mode is not supported. Ensure
                        that the host is set to use Legacy BIOS mode. For details, refer to the
                        documentation supplied with your hardware. </p>
                </note>
            </section>
